
  ==========================
   logi.crypto java package
  ==========================

This file should be distributed with four other files:

  logi.crypto.jar  A jar file containing the logi.crypto package
  
  src.zip          The complete source code for the package
  
  doc.zip          Documentation, including javadocs for the package
  
  fingerprint      Fingerprints of the above fies gneerated with
                   the org.logi.crypto.test.hash utility

Most likely you will want to place cryptonite.jar in your classpath and
unzip doc.zip. Then use your web-browser to read doc/index.html.

Updates will be available on http://www.logi.org/logi.crypto

Send any questions or suggestions to logir@logi.org

Thank you,
Logi Ragnarsson
